{"lastModified":1751916224119,"uri":"c::8344947358::vessel::d5cc4f71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThis stunning 560 S2 Lagoon S/Y BOOM ensures comfort and style, while her professional crew of three will pamper you, ensuring that you have the most memorable cruising experience. From her lovely flybridge and al fresco dining area, to her shaded spaces on the main deck and the sunbathing trampolines forward, this spacious catamaran covers every base for relaxation and entertainment. Designed by world-renowned talents of the architectural firm VPLP and the consultants Nauta, S/Y BOOM has been created for\nhospitable cruising. She is fully equipped with a Hi-Fi system linked to cockpit, saloon and flybridge speakers, ice-maker, USB sockets in the cabins and underwater lights. The cockpit is fully protected from the sun and sea spray and is on the same level as the galley cuisine, fully air-conditioned saloon and chart table. Transom platforms are specially designed for safe boarding on the dinghy and give easy access to the crystal blue sea when swimming. She has four fully air-conditioned VIP double cabins, all with en-suite\nbathrooms. The cabins are spacious with storage areas for guests, ensuring maximum comfort and privacy. S/Y BOOM is packed with toys, including a 4.2m Highfield Delux tender with a powerful 60HP outdoor motor and two seabobs, which will keep the guests entertained all day. Her generator keeps electricity flowing and ensures air-conditioning and electrical appliances keep running, even when the main engines are shut down, so you can enjoy every bit of your holiday even when anchored in a secluded bay.","blueprint":{"name":"BOOM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::33d681e0-a264-11ef-81b2-272f98628d73/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::339ea900-a264-11ef-81b2-272